The aesthetics are incredible  and the grounds are gorgeous- and SO secure.
The manager, Leslie, was very informative and helpful.
The location does not seem ideal in the least bit, being more towards the suburbs.
But, the building itself has more to offer than most comparable high-rises.
I love it.

