The Modern had a large bill to fill with my wife and I coming from LA.
It has done that and more.
Probably the only kind of modern living at this level in Las Vegas.
It's within great proximity to the strip so if you want to get get crazy it's a safe cab ride away.
And far enough removed that you don't feel as tho your the center attraction in a 3 ring circus.
The amenities and architecture are just what they claim to be....Modern.
Great thing about that all of our furniture fit just perfectly being that's exactly what our tastes are.
A great management team with friendly and prompt service round out a great living experience.
I highly suggest giving this place a look if your in the market to buy or rent.

